(16, 'Sử dụng mạng xã hội thông minh sẽ giúp bạn an toàn', 4, '<h1 class=\"post-title\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(29, 29, 29); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 36px; line-height: 40px; font-family: Roboto-Bold, sans-serif;\">Sử dụng mạng xã hội thông minh sẽ giúp bạn an toàn</h1><h4 class=\"post-publishdate\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 15px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-transform: uppercase; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; font-family: Roboto-Medium, sans-serif; float: left;\"><a class=\"post-author\" href=\"https://thoidai.com.vn/search_enginer.html?p=tim-kiem&amp;q=Linh%20San&amp;s_cond=3\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Linh San</a>&nbsp;<span class=\"post-author-2\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-transform: none;\">đăng lúc</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"date\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">30/12/2020 14:49</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"separate\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 1px;\">|&nbsp;</span><a class=\"post-cat\" href=\"https://thoidai.com.vn/nhan-quyen/hoi-tho-cuoc-song\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(171, 30, 36);\">HƠI THỞ CUỘC SỐNG</a></h4><div class=\"post-social fw lt clearfix\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; float: left; width: 730px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"fb-like lt fb_iframe_widget\" data-href=\"https://thoidai.com.vn/su-dung-mang-xa-hoi-thong-minh-se-giup-ban-an-toan-127516.html\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-action=\"like\" data-size=\"small\" data-show-faces=\"false\" data-share=\"true\" fb-xfbml-state=\"rendered\" fb-iframe-plugin-query=\"action=like&amp;app_id=430169401059835&amp;container_width=0&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fthoidai.com.vn%2Fsu-dung-mang-xa-hoi-thong-minh-se-gi